<br>
I have re-arranged the spell list with some changes, but I would like to fill out our list with a new effect.<br>
<br>
Here are the rules:<br>
1. Song is either a shout or a chant. It can either be offensive and do something to an enemy or be defensive and do something to yourself or your group.<br>
<br>
2. It must not be a direct steal from another class.  It can be a variation of an ability from another realm.<br>
<br>
3. It must not be ridiculous. Please, serious and well thought out responses only.<br>
<br>
Rosey<br>
