<br>
1) First increase range on current chants (if not shouts and chants), combine resists, and increase damage add.  This concept can be seen as making 2 new chants b/c damage add and resist chant will be very different.<br>
<br>
AND<br>
<br>
2) New chant: Absorption Chant that can scale up.  Im not a numbers cruncher but start with say 5% at lowest level in BS and scale up to say 25% (1/2 of BoF I think).  Make last one at say 48 BS or something so that BS line is worth taking past 46.  Hell with damage add as is its not even worth going past 44.  Make sure the range of this is NOT a laughable 700 like most of our shouts/chants.<br>
<br>
OR<br>
<br>
2) New Shout: Something that can be done on keep defense/offense.  Replace our snare and lower level dd with a long range dd/root (root, not snare) type shout.  <br>
<br>
Im saying 1 AND 2 would be needed but these are 2 ideas in ADDITION to #1. <br>
<br>
Now some people are asking for a haste chant.  This is not a bad idea but isnt going to address the decent offense/lack of defense problem we face.  Haste is good but since we drop so fast due to poor defense it wont help much.<br>
<br>
The one thing I can say with absolute certitude is we do NOT want a power regen chant.  I hear midgardians on certain VN boards be-moaning this (I understand) b/c others realm have a castable version and chantable version of pow regen.  If midgard gets another pow regen it will be a chant.  If its a chant guess who mythic will wanna give it to considering skalds are saying we need something.<br>
<br>
