<br>
2)  Change our Resist Chants to Resist/Reflection Chants.  For example if Fire Chant 1 (10%) is up, then 10% of fire damage done is reflected back at the caster.  <br>
<br>
This is powerful for two reasons.  i)  It will interupt the caster from chain casting.  ii)  AE's hitting your whole group and reflecting back will do major damage to that caster.<br>
<br>
Reflection will do nothing for binary spells like Mez and Root.<br>
<br>
Sideshow lvl50 skald<br>
