<br>
This new spell list has open spaces for a new song, which is why we need an idea for a good song to fill in the spots.  The open levels for the new song are 8,16,24,34,44 if that helps anyone.<br>
<br>
There are some good ideas so far, but let's see if we can get even more, then hash out the most popular.<br>
<br>
I originally thought a knock-back and untarget shout would have been nice (knock the target back xx units per level and remove targetting) but after thinking on it, it is fraught with many problems, namely which would be doing more damage than intended if you knock someone back on a keep or a steep incline (falling damage).<br>
<br>
Anyway, don't worry, range and resists have been reworked in my dream upgraded spell list.  I want to get this together as soon as possible to send it in to the correct people.<br>
<br>
(I am directly sending it this time, as well as sending the updated abilities and items to the other responsible parties)<br>
